<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed); padding: 32px; text-align: center; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Welcome to ReZum!</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="background: white; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none;">
    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">
      Thanks for joining ReZum! You're all set to start optimizing your resume with AI and landing more interviews.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Here's how to get started:</p>

    <div style="margin: 24px 0;">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <span style="background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;">1</span>
        <div>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Upload your resume</p>
          <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">PDF, DOCX, or TXT — we'll extract and parse it instantly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <span style="background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;">2</span>
        <div>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Paste a job description</p>
          <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Our AI tailors your resume specifically for the role.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start;">
        <span style="background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;">3</span>
        <div>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Get your optimized resume</p>
          <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">See your ATS score improvement and download in PDF/DOCX.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
      You have <strong style="color: #2563eb;"><%= @user.credits_remaining %> free credits</strong> to get started. Each optimization uses 1 credit.
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
      <a href="<%= dashboard_url %>" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed); color: white; padding: 12px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;">
        Go to Dashboard
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 16px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
    <p>ReZum — AI-Powered Resume Optimization</p>
  </div>
</div>
